.\" docs/man/meow-config.5
.TH MEOW-CONFIG 5 "2025-09-19" "meowg1k" "File Formats"
.SH NAME
meow-config \- configuration for the \fBmeow\fR CLI (YAML)
.SH SYNOPSIS
Configuration is read from YAML files with the following precedence:
.IP "1." 3
Explicit config: specified via \fB\-\-config\fR flag (overrides all)
.IP "2."
Project config: \fB./.meowg1k/config.yaml\fR
.IP "3."
User config: \fB~/.config/meowg1k/config.yaml\fR
.PP
When \fB\-\-config\fR is used, only that file is loaded, ignoring project and user configs completely.
.SH DESCRIPTION
The \fBmeow\fR CLI uses a profile\-based YAML configuration system to define
reusable provider configurations and tasks. Supports Anthropic Claude, Voyage AI embeddings,
and comprehensive model registry with automatic tokenizer detection.
.SH FORMAT
YAML, UTF-8.
.PP
Configuration structure:
.PP
.nf
profiles:
  <profile-name>:
    provider: "gemini" | "openai" | "openrouter" | "nebius" | "anthropic" | "voyage" | "llama" | "openai-compatible"
    model: "model-name"              # optional, uses smart defaults
    baseURL: "https://api.url"       # required for llama/openai-compatible
    apiKeyEnv: "ENV_VAR_NAME"        # optional, uses smart defaults
    maxInputTokens: 8192             # optional, default 8192
    timeout: "5m"                    # optional, default 5m

generate:
  default:
    profile: "profile-name"          # default profile to use
    systemPrompt: "System instruction"
  tasks:
    <task-name>:
      profile: "profile-name"        # optional, uses default
      systemPrompt: "Task-specific system prompt"
      userPrompt: "Task-specific user prompt"
.fi
.SH KEYS
.TP
.B profiles
Map of reusable provider configurations. Each profile defines:
.RS
.IP \[bu] 2
\fBprovider\fR: Provider type (required)
.IP \[bu]
\fBmodel\fR: Model name (optional, uses smart defaults)
.IP \[bu]
\fBbaseURL\fR: Base URL (required for llama/openai-compatible)
.IP \[bu]
\fBapiKeyEnv\fR: Environment variable name (optional, uses smart defaults)
.IP \[bu]
\fBmaxInputTokens\fR: Token limit (optional, default 8192)
.IP \[bu]
\fBtimeout\fR: Request timeout (optional, default 5m)
.RE
.TP
.B generate.default
Default settings for generation:
.RS
.IP \[bu] 2
\fBprofile\fR: Default profile name to use
.IP \[bu]
\fBsystemPrompt\fR: Default system instruction
.RE
.TP
.B generate.tasks
Map of predefined tasks. Each task can override:
.RS
.IP \[bu] 2
\fBprofile\fR: Profile to use (optional, uses default)
.IP \[bu]
\fBsystemPrompt\fR: Task-specific system instruction
.IP \[bu]
\fBuserPrompt\fR: Task-specific user prompt
.RE

.SH PROVIDER DEFAULTS
Each provider has smart defaults:
.TP
.B gemini
Model: \fBgemini-2.5-flash\fR, API key: \fBMEOW_GEMINI_API_KEY\fR
.TP
.B openai
Model: \fBgpt-5-mini\fR, API key: \fBMEOW_OPENAI_API_KEY\fR
.TP
.B openrouter
Model: \fBmeta-llama/llama-3.2-3b-instruct:free\fR, API key: \fBMEOW_OPENROUTER_API_KEY\fR
.TP
.B nebius
Model: \fBQwen2.5-Coder-7B\fR, API key: \fBMEOW_NEBIUS_API_KEY\fR
.TP
.B anthropic
Model: \fBclaude-3-5-haiku-20241022\fR, API key: \fBMEOW_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY\fR
.TP
.B voyage
Model: \fBvoyage-3.5\fR, API key: \fBMEOW_VOYAGE_API_KEY\fR (embeddings only)
.TP
.B llama
API key: \fBMEOW_LLAMA_API_KEY\fR (requires explicit baseURL)
.TP
.B openai-compatible
API key: \fBMEOW_OPENAI_COMPATIBLE_API_KEY\fR (requires explicit baseURL)

.SH EXAMPLES
Minimal profile-based config:
.PP
.nf
profiles:
  fast:
    provider: "gemini"
  smart:
    provider: "openai"
    model: "gpt-4o"

generate:
  default:
    profile: "fast"
.fi
.PP
Full project config with tasks:
.PP
.nf
profiles:
  review:
    provider: "openai"
    model: "gpt-4o"
    maxInputTokens: 32768
  local:
    provider: "llama"
    baseURL: "http://localhost:8080"

generate:
  default:
    profile: "review"
  tasks:
    security:
      profile: "review"
      userPrompt: "Review for security vulnerabilities"
    test:
      profile: "local"
      userPrompt: "Write comprehensive tests"
.fi
.PP
Advanced configuration with additional providers:
.PP
.nf
profiles:
  anthropic-smart:
    provider: "anthropic"
    model: "claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022"
    maxInputTokens: 32000
    timeout: "10m"

  voyage-embeddings:
    provider: "voyage"
    model: "voyage-3.5"
    # Note: Voyage is embeddings-only

  custom-api:
    provider: "openai-compatible"
    baseURL: "https://api.custom-llm.com/v1"
    model: "custom-model-70b"
    apiKeyEnv: "CUSTOM_API_KEY"

generate:
  default:
    profile: "anthropic-smart"
  tasks:
    deep-review:
      profile: "anthropic-smart"
      userPrompt: "Perform comprehensive code analysis"
.fi

